### Create a space quota

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/space_quotas" \
  -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]" \
  -H "Content-type: application/json" \
  -d '{
        "name": "production",
        "relationships": {
          "organization": {
            "data": {
              "guid": "[org-guid]"
            }
          }
        }
      }'
```

